Name: Gorilla Unko
About the game: You are the cleaning staff of the zoo. There is only one goal in 'Gorilla Unko'. Keep avoiding the gorilla's UNKO as much as you can. The more you avoid, the higher the score will become. Compete high scores with world through online rankings.
